{
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, integrating GAI into ISAC undergoes some obstacles.",
    "First, training the GAI models can be time-consuming because of its complicated network architecture and the enormous number of parameters, hindering its applications in the scenarios with low-latency requirements.",
    "Second, GAI models often need large-scale computation and communication resources to train and infer, posing a huge challenge in practical ISAC systems.",
    "Therefore, it is necessary to investigate the effective deployment scheme for GAI-enabled ISAC systems.",
    "AI-enabled THz-ISACThanks to the ultra-broad bandwidth (0.1-10 THz), terahertz (THz) can achieve terabit-per-second-level transmission rate and millimeter-level sensing accuracy [273]."
  ]
}